==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''hydrocephalus'''

#{{uncountable}} {{medicine}} A usually [[congenital]] [[condition]] in which an [[abnormal]] [[accumulation]] of [[fluid]] in the [[cerebral]] [[ventricle|ventricles]] causes [[enlargement]] of the skull and compression of the brain, destroying much of the [[neural]] tissue

====Synonyms====
*[[water on the brain]] (''informal'')

